31 2. For at least the first 15 calendar days after the signage is
32 installed.
33 (2) (i) A noise abatement monitoring system operator shall complete
34 training by the manufacturer of the noise abatement monitoring system in the procedures
35 for setting up and operating the noise abatement monitoring system.

